 582:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  Structure parameters    |               Description
 583:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *--------------------------|--------------------------------------------------
 584:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | By enabling this bit, accel data according to the
 585:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  data_reg_en             | user defined accel configuration is taken for tap
 586:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | detector feature.
 587:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
 588:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  tap_sens_thres          | Scaling factor of additional threshold increment
 589:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | for detection of positive and negative peak of tap.
 590:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
 591:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  max_gest_dur            | Maximum duration after the first tap within which the
 592:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | second and/or third tap have to be performed for being
 593:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | detected as double-tap.
 594:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
 595:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  quite_time_after_gest   | Minimum quite time between the two gesture detection.
 596:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
 597:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @endverbatim
 598:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *
