1149:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Value 2       - low asymmetrical
1150:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1151:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Enable - no orientation interrupt will be set.
1152:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *      blocking            | Default value: 3, the most restrictive blocking.
1153:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1154:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Threshold angle used in blocking mode.
1155:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *      theta               | Theta = 64 * (tan(angle)^2)
1156:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Default value: 40, equivalent to 38 degrees angle.
1157:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1158:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Acceleration hysteresis for Orientation detection
1159:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | is expressed in 5.11g format.
1160:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *      hysteresis          | Default value is 128 = 0.0625g.
1161:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Range is 0 to 1g.
1162:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1163:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @endverbatim
1164:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *
1165:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @return Result of API execution status
1166:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @retval 0 -> Success
1167:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @retval < 0 -> Fail
1168:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  */
