1182:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *--------------------------|--------------------------------------------------
1183:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *      threshold           |  The acceleration threshold above which the
1184:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          |  high_g motion is signaled.
1185:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          |  Threshold value for high_g feature.
1186:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          |  Range is 0 to 16g.
1187:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          |  Default value is 10000 = 4.9g.
1188:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1189:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Hysteresis value for high_g feature.
1190:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *      hysteresis          | Range is 0 to 2g.
1191:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Default value is 1000 = 0.49g.
1192:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1193:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Holds the duration in 200 Hz samples (5 ms) for
1194:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | which the threshold has to be exceeded.
1195:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *      duration            | Default value 4 = 20 msec.
1196:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Range is 0 to 20sec.
