1373:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @brief This internal API gets step counter/detector/activity configurations.
1374:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *
1375:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @param[out] config      : Structure instance of bmi2_step_config.
1376:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @param[in]  dev         : Structure instance of bmi2_dev.
1377:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *
1378:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @verbatim
1379:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *----------------------------------------------------------------------------
1380:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *    bmi2_step_config      |
1381:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  Structure parameters    |                 Description
1382:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *--------------------------|--------------------------------------------------
1383:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | The Step-counter will trigger output every time
1384:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | the number of steps are counted. Holds implicitly
1385:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  water-mark level        | a 20x factor, so the range is 0 to 10230,
1386:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | with resolution of 20 steps.
1387:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1388:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  reset counter           | Flag to reset the counted steps.
1389:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1390:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @endverbatim
