1498:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *
1499:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @verbatim
1500:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *    bmi2_low_g_config     |
1501:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *   Structure parameters   |               Description
1502:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *--------------------------|--------------------------------------------------
1503:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  threshold               |  The acceleration threshold above which the
1504:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          |  low-g motion is signaled.
1505:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          |  Holds threshold in 5.11 g format.
1506:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          |  Default is 3072 = 1.5 g.
1507:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1508:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          |  Acceleration hysteresis for low-g detection
1509:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  hysteresis              | is expressed in 1.11g format.
1510:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Default value is 512 = 0.250 g.
1511:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Should be smaller than threshold.
1512:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
ARM GAS  /var/folders/gv/t2w3mcd17yl2fynvjl120d0m0000gn/T//ccDW1WpJ.s 			page 28


1513:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Holds the duration in 50 Hz samples (20 ms) for
1514:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | which the threshold has to be exceeded.
1515:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  duration                | Default value 0 = 1 validation sample = (0+1)*20
1516:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | = 20 ms.
1517:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1518:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @endverbatim
1519:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *
1520:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @return Result of API execution status
1521:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @retval 0 -> Success
