1526:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c **** /*!
1527:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @brief This internal API gets flat configurations like theta, blocking,
1528:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * hold-time, hysteresis, and output configuration.
1529:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *
