1537:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *--------------------------|--------------------------------------------------
1538:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Theta angle, used for detecting flat
1539:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | position.
1540:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *      theta               | Theta = 64 * (tan(angle)^2);
1541:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Default value is 8, equivalent to 20 degrees angle
1542:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1543:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Hysteresis for Theta Flat detection.
1544:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *      hysteresis          | Default value is 9 = 2.5 degrees, corresponding
1545:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | to the default Theta angle of 20 degrees.
1546:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1547:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Sets the blocking mode. If blocking is set, no
1548:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Flat interrupt will be triggered.
1549:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *      blocking            | Default value is 2, the most restrictive blocking
1550:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | mode.
1551:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1552:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Holds the duration in 50Hz samples for which the
1553:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | condition has to be respected.
1554:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *      hold-time           | Default value is 32 = 640 m-sec.
1555:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *                          | Range is 0 to 5.1 sec.
1556:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * -------------------------|---------------------------------------------------
1557:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @endverbatim
1558:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *
1559:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @return Result of API execution status
1560:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @retval 0 -> Success
1561:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  * @retval < 0 -> Fail
