1819:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c **** /*!
1820:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  @brief This API:
1821:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  1) Updates the device structure with address of the configuration file.
1822:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  2) Initializes BMI270_LEGACY sensor.
1823:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  3) Writes the configuration file.
1824:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  4) Updates the feature offset parameters in the device structure.
1825:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270_legacy.c ****  *  5) Updates the maximum number of pages, in the device structure.
